# 9. Price History

V1 espone i prezzi nella valuta della Listing. Il servizio può memorizzare Listing in valute diverse, ma non fornisce tassi FX o conversione valutaria in v1. I consumer sono responsabili della propria policy valutaria.

V1 stores daily unadjusted OHLCV prices only. Intraday synchronisation may refresh the current trading day's daily bar, but the service does not expose intraday bars in v1. When supplied by a Data Provider, an optional adjusted close may be stored; v1 does not calculate adjusted OHLCV internally.

Observed prices can be provisional or final. The current trading day's daily bar is provisional until the trading day is complete and the provider data is settled. Latest price endpoints return the freshest available observed price, whether provisional or final, and include its status in the response.

```json
{
  "listing_id": "...",
  "date": "2026-06-01",
  "open": 8.10,
  "high": 8.20,
  "low": 8.05,
  "close": 8.18,
  "adjusted_close": 8.12,
  "volume": 1200000,
  "status": "final"
}
```

